s improvement. Use when: (1) A command or        │                  │\n│               │                       │ operation fails unexpectedly, (2) User corrects Claude    │                  │\n│               │                       │ ('No, that's wrong...', 'Actually...'), (3) User          │                  │\n│               │                       │ requests a capability that doesn't exist, (4) An          │                  │\n│               │                       │ external API or tool fails, (5) Claude realizes its       │                  │\n│               │                       │ knowledge is outdated or incorrect, (6) A better          │                  │\n│               │                       │ approach is discovered for a recurring task. Also review  │                  │\n│               │                       │ learnings before major tasks.                             │                  │\n└───────────────┴───────────────────────┴───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┴──────────────────┘\n\nTip: use `openclaw skills search`, `openclaw skills install`, and `openclaw skills update` for ClawHub-backed skills.","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774932326196}}
{"type":"message","id":"3a616fab","parentId":"569c7543","timestamp":"2026-03-31T04:45:43.719Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"列表显示有55个技能，其中15个已就绪（✓ ready）。用户可能想安装一些“必备”技能。哪些是必备的呢？这取决于用户的需求。但也许一些常用的技能，比如 `github`、`healthcheck`、`node-connect`、`openai-whisper`、`session-logs`、`skill-creator`、`tmux`、`video-frames`、`weather` 已经就绪了。不过，还有 `feishu-*` 技能（文档、云端硬盘、权限、Wiki）也已经就绪。\n\n用户可能想安装所有缺失的技能，但那样会很多。也许他们指的是安装 ClawHub 上的社区技能。但“必备技能”这个说法可能指的是 OpenClaw 运行所需的核心技能。不过，OpenClaw 本身似乎已经包含了这些技能，只是有些需要设置（`needs setup`）。这些技能可能已经安装了，但缺少配置或依赖。\n\n我可以询问用户具体需要哪些技能，或者提供指导。考虑到用户是通过 Webchat 控制界面提问的，他们可能希望我自动安装一些推荐技能。但为了安全起见，我应该先征求他们的同意。\n\n让我先检查一下 `openclaw skills install` 的用法。看看是否需要指定技能名称。也许有办法批量安装。但首先，我需要知道用户想要什么。\n\n我可以这样回复：我已经有很多技能了，有些已经就绪，有些需要设置。询问他们具体想安装哪些技能，或者是否需要我推荐一些核心技能。\n\n但用户问的是“你现在可以做到给我安装你的必备技能吗”，这可能意味着他们希望我自动安装必备技能。我可以尝试安装一些常见的技能，比如 `clawhub`（用于管理技能）、`coding-agent`、`gemini` 等。但我不确定。\n\n让我先看看 `openclaw skills install` 命令的帮助信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_4ASjiIB4roR2zPoFa5o07Snx","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/openclaw skills install --help"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":4839,"output":849,"cacheRead":19264,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24952,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774932326203,"responseId":"ec35a79c-4982-4947-a61f-93c81f10f2ef"}}
