{"type":"message","id":"7878c1cf","parentId":"a1cac67d","timestamp":"2026-03-31T05:17:08.199Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"当前目录就是OpenClaw的工作区。但用户可能想知道他们自己的项目目录在哪里。在OpenClaw中，coding‑agent技能通常需要一个工作目录（workdir）参数。如果没有指定，可能会在当前目录运行。\n\n让我读取一下coding‑agent的SKILL.md，看看它关于工作目录的说明。之前读过了，里面提到“workdir matters: Agent wakes up in a focused directory”。但用户问的是“项目目录在哪”，这可能是在问OpenClaw控制UI的项目目录，或者是系统上的项目目录。\n\n我需要先澄清问题。也许用户指的是OpenClaw控制UI中“项目”的概念。但根据上下文，更可能的是用户想知道他们自己的代码项目存储在哪里。\n\n让我检查一下用户家目录的常见项目位置。用ls查看。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_pT6D4uS1LEqEsiXOuZw1pIfL","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/ | grep -E \"(Projects|projects|workspace|code|src)\" | head -10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":240,"output":389,"cacheRead":36928,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37557,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774934219445,"responseId":"aac203a7-4c93-4cb1-9ea8-1c4f4b079ae4"}}
