en each learning appears in `.learnings/LEARNINGS.md`\n+ 76 2. **Promote high-frequency learnings**: When the same learning appears 3 or more times, summarize it and add it to the appropriate section of `AGENTS.md` (e.g., under \"Tools\", \"Memory\", or a new dedicated section)\n+ 77 3. **Archive promoted learnings**: After promoting a learning to `AGENTS.md`, you may optionally move or delete the original record from `.learnings/LEARNINGS.md` to keep it concise\n+ 78 4. **Regular maintenance**: During heartbeat checks, spend a few minutes reviewing and organizing the `.learnings/` directory\n+ 79 \n  48 ## Red Lines\n  49 \n  50 - Don't exfiltrate private data. Ever.\n  51 - Don't run destructive commands without asking.\n     ...","firstChangedLine":48},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774942411612}}
