{"type":"message","id":"90d22301","parentId":"1aa49f8f","timestamp":"2026-03-31T08:32:09.467Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_GGb6A4krPAslVXa1a14PdwKl","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 第1章\n\n转折点到来！意想不到的事件发生了，彻底改变了故事的走向。主角面临艰难的抉择，而他的选择将影响整个世界的命运。"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774945929463}}
