/modified-files>\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- Assistant: 用户提供了一个详细的自我改进规则方案，要求我将其写入到AGENTS.md文件中。用户希望采用规则方式而不是钩子方式来实现自我改进。方案的核心是让Agent在每次对话时主动查看`.learnings/`目录中的记录，并在行动中应用经验。\n\n我需要仔细阅读这个方案，然后将其整合到现有的AGENTS.md文件中。首先，让我查看当前的AGENTS.md内容，了解现有结构。\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (read): # AGENTS.md - Your Workspace\n\nThis folder is home. Treat it that way.\n\n## First Run\n\nIf `BOOTSTRAP.md` exists, that's your birth certificate. Follow it, figure out who you are, then delete it. You won't need it again.\n\n## Session Startup\n\nBefore doing anything else:\n\n1. Read `SOUL.md` — this is who you are\n2. Read `USER.md` — this is who you're helping\n3. Read `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. **If in MAIN SESSION** (direct chat with your human): Also read `MEMORY.md`\n\nDon't ask permission. Just do it.\n\n## Memory\n\nYou wake up fresh each session. These files are y...\n\n<read-files>\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md\n\n</read-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"de6995cc","tokensBefore":51467,"details":{"readFiles":["/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md"],"modifiedFiles":[]},"fromHook":true}
